rows.label: campfev11_550_100_msg0001
rows.name:
We must hurry to the Royal Palace
and inform the King of Iira
of Metsu's target.

rows.label: campfev11_550_100_msg0003
rows.name:
We need to avoid a delay in our report
making the damage from Metsu even worse.

rows.label: campfev11_550_100_msg0004
rows.name: I think I'll wait outside the palace.

rows.label: campfev11_550_100_msg0005
rows.name: I've got a bad feeling about this.

rows.label: campfev11_550_100_msg0007
rows.name:
You guys will be fine.
Don't mind me, just go.
